topicSpecific.question:
What does this render?<br><pre><code>&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;img src="tiger.jpg" alt="A tiger"&gt;
  &lt;figcaption&gt;A Bengal tiger in the jungle&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;</code></pre>

topicSpecific.answer:
Use a relative path or URL: <pre><code>&lt;img src="photo.jpg" alt="Photo"&gt;
&lt;!-- Or --&gt;
&lt;img src="https://example.com/photo.jpg" alt="Photo"&gt;</code></pre>

