&lt;img src="huge2.jpg"&gt;
&lt;img src="huge3.jpg"&gt;</code></pre>

mixed.answer:
Add alt attributes, use properly sized image files, and add loading="lazy":<pre><code>&lt;img src="photo1.jpg" alt="Photo 1" width="400" loading="lazy"&gt;
&lt;img src="photo2.jpg" alt="Photo 2" width="400" loading="lazy"&gt;
&lt;img src="photo3.jpg" alt="Photo 3" width="400" loading="lazy"&gt;</code></pre>
